= Scientific activities

== Organization
- Lead organizer of the [https://sites.google.com/site/youngresearcherssummerschool/ 2nd /Young researchers summer school/] for PhD students of CEREMADE in september 2016 (gathered 16 participants during 1 week).
- Organizer of the [https://sites.google.com/site/jeuneschercheursceremade/ /Weekly seminar for young researchers/]  at CEREMADE for years 2015-2016, with [https://sites.google.com/site/labordemax2/ Maxime Laborde].

